<p class="MsoToc1"><span class="MsoHyperlink"><span lang="EN-GB" style="mso-no-proof:yes" xml:lang="EN-GB">
<a href="#_Toc994820252"><b>Annex C</b> (informative) <b>Bibliography</b><span lang="EN-GB" class="MsoTocTextSpan" xml:lang="EN-GB">
