        <br clear="all" style="mso-special-character:line-break;page-break-before:always"/>
      </p>
      <div class="Section3">
        <a name="annex-abstract-test-suite" id="annex-abstract-test-suite"></a>
        <h1 class="Annex"><b>Annex A</b><br/>(normative)<br/><b>Abstract Test Suite</b></h1>
        <p style="display:none;" class="variant-title-toc">Annex A<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>Abstract Test Suite</p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><a name="_8c5f0d04-5453-5b51-4a7e-779a3832994b" id="_8c5f0d04-5453-5b51-4a7e-779a3832994b"></a>Tests and requirement identifiers below are relative to <b><a href="http://www.opengis.net/spec/WPS/2.0">http://www.opengis.net/spec/WPS/2.0</a></b></p>
        <div><a name="annex-subsec-basic-wps-conformace-class" id="annex-subsec-basic-wps-conformace-class"></a><h2>A.1.<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>Basic WPS (Conformance Class)</h2>

<p style="page-break-after:avoid;" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_d43b39b2-fd91-d167-a905-4242d4a85dbc" id="_d43b39b2-fd91-d167-a905-4242d4a85dbc"></a>The OGC URI identifier of this conformance class is: <b><a href="http://www.opengis.net/spec/WPS/2.0/conf/service/profile/basic-wps">http://www.opengis.net/spec/WPS/2.0/conf/service/profile/basic-wps</a></b></p>

<p class="SourceTitle" style="text-align:center;">Example</p><div class="example"><a name="_0d3295ef-4eef-5bc1-1fed-b70ced6adddf" id="_0d3295ef-4eef-5bc1-1fed-b70ced6adddf"></a><div class="require"><a name="_a92f2bb6-1b3e-4ff5-a6d1-6c4625f966f9" id="_a92f2bb6-1b3e-4ff5-a6d1-6c4625f966f9"></a><div align="center" class="table_container"><table class="MsoISOTable" style="mso-table-anchor-horizontal:column;mso-table-overlap:never;border-spacing:0;border-width:1px;" width="100%"><a name="_69f185ff-2923-8695-9d74-a8ccca481df4" id="_69f185ff-2923-8695-9d74-a8ccca481df4"></a><thead><tr><th colspan="2" style="font-weight:bold;border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:avoid;"><p class="RecommendationTitle" style="page-break-after:avoid">Requirement A.1</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><th style="font-weight:bold;border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;">Statement</th><td style="border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;"><p style="page-break-after:auto" class="example"><a name="_a78567ce-9f4d-e95b-c380-2e9404d685b9" id="_a78567ce-9f4d-e95b-c380-2e9404d685b9"></a>conf/service/profile/basic-wps</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>

<div class="recommend"><a name="_657ad696-c0b5-4af8-b52a-2d4e8568e891" id="_657ad696-c0b5-4af8-b52a-2d4e8568e891"></a><div align="center" class="table_container"><table class="MsoISOTable" style="mso-table-anchor-horizontal:column;mso-table-overlap:never;border-spacing:0;border-width:1px;" width="100%"><a name="_aeec36ba-6b80-7dad-140a-3731e8cab9b7" id="_aeec36ba-6b80-7dad-140a-3731e8cab9b7"></a><thead><tr><th colspan="2" style="font-weight:bold;border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:avoid;"><p class="RecommendationTitle" style="page-break-after:avoid">Recommendation A.1</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><th style="font-weight:bold;border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;">Statement</th><td style="border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;"><p style="page-break-after:auto" class="example"><a name="_12515c46-f0a7-f572-0f4a-09e5cdbad336" id="_12515c46-f0a7-f572-0f4a-09e5cdbad336"></a>Verify that the server implements the Basic WPS conformance class.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>

<div class="require"><a name="_acd82a68-5095-4a86-ad18-5364bf695cbd" id="_acd82a68-5095-4a86-ad18-5364bf695cbd"></a><div align="center" class="table_container"><table class="MsoISOTable" style="mso-table-anchor-horizontal:column;mso-table-overlap:never;border-spacing:0;border-width:1px;" width="100%"><a name="_8d96c506-2459-cfce-43ab-eb895558c366" id="_8d96c506-2459-cfce-43ab-eb895558c366"></a><thead><tr><th colspan="2" style="font-weight:bold;border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:avoid;"><p class="RecommendationTitle" style="page-break-after:avoid">Requirement A.2</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><th style="font-weight:bold;border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;">Statement</th><td style="border-top:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;"><p style="page-break-after:auto" class="example"><a name="_8cb15b74-3291-8454-f86c-80768b571ffc" id="_8cb15b74-3291-8454-f86c-80768b571ffc"></a>Verify that the server implements the Synchronous WPS and/or the Asynchronous WPS conformance class. Verify that the requests and responses to a supported operation are syntactically correct. Verify that the service supports the Synchronous WPS Conformance class, the Asynchronous WPS Conformance class or both. Verify that all process offerings implement the native process model.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>
</div>
</div>
      </div>
      <p class="MsoNormal">
        <br clear="all" style="mso-special-character:line-break;page-break-before:always"/>
      </p>
      <div class="Section3">
        <a name="annex-xml-examples" id="annex-xml-examples"></a>
        <h1 class="Annex"><b>Annex B</b><br/>(informative)<br/><b>XML Examples</b></h1>
        <p style="display:none;" class="variant-title-toc">Annex B<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>XML Examples</p>
        <div><a name="annex-subsec-data-types" id="annex-subsec-data-types"></a><h2>B.1.<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>Data Types</h2>

<div><a name="_c93605c4-e2ef-a95d-fcb7-9b69d0213358" id="_c93605c4-e2ef-a95d-fcb7-9b69d0213358"></a><h3>B.1.1.<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>Complex Data Description</h3>

<p class="Sourcecode"><a name="_f3de7c61-ec11-fb12-135d-f7e322f1c7dc" id="_f3de7c61-ec11-fb12-135d-f7e322f1c7dc"></a><span class="nt">&lt;wps:ComplexData&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;wps:Format</span> <span class="na">mimeType=</span><span class="s">"application/geotiff"</span> <span class="na">encoding=</span><span class="s">"raw"</span><br/><span class="na">default=</span><span class="s">"true"</span><span class="nt">/&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;wps:Format</span> <span class="na">mimeType=</span><span class="s">"application/geotiff"</span> <span class="na">encoding=</span><span class="s">"base64"</span><span class="nt">/&gt;</span><br/><span class="nt">&lt;/wps:ComplexData&gt;</span></p>

</div>

<div><a name="_c8cba9aa-0b70-26be-9330-cacdf515eeb3" id="_c8cba9aa-0b70-26be-9330-cacdf515eeb3"></a><h3>B.1.2.<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>Literal Data Description</h3>

<p class="Sourcecode"><a name="_cd380b6a-50ce-3caf-577d-7a349705d9ed" id="_cd380b6a-50ce-3caf-577d-7a349705d9ed"></a><span class="nt">&lt;wps:LiteralData&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;wps:Format</span> <span class="na">mimeType=</span><span class="s">"text/plain"</span> <span class="na">default=</span><span class="s">"true"</span><span class="nt">/&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;wps:Format</span> <span class="na">mimeType=</span><span class="s">"text/xml"</span><span class="nt">/&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;LiteralDataDomain</span> <span class="na">default=</span><span class="s">"true"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:AllowedValues&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:Range&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:MinimumValue&gt;</span>1<span class="nt">&lt;/ows:MinimumValue&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:MaximumValue&gt;</span>1000<span class="nt">&lt;/ows:MaximumValue&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;/ows:Range&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;/ows:AllowedValues&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:DataType</span><br/><span class="na">ows:reference=</span><span class="s">"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#float"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>float<br/><span class="nt">&lt;/ows:DataType&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:UOM&gt;</span>meters<span class="nt">&lt;/ows:UOM&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:DefaultValue&gt;</span>100<span class="nt">&lt;/ows:DefaultValue&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;/LiteralDataDomain&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;LiteralDataDomain&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:AllowedValues&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:Range&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:MinimumValue&gt;</span>1<span class="nt">&lt;/ows:MinimumValue&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:MaximumValue&gt;</span>3000<span class="nt">&lt;/ows:MaximumValue&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;/ows:Range&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;/ows:AllowedValues&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:DataType</span><br/><span class="na">ows:reference=</span><span class="s">"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#float"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>float<br/><span class="nt">&lt;/ows:DataType&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:UOM&gt;</span>feet<span class="nt">&lt;/ows:UOM&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;/LiteralDataDomain&gt;</span><br/><span class="nt">&lt;/wps:LiteralData&gt;</span></p>

</div>

<div><a name="_3de25ba3-1474-aafa-fb04-59bd58732ffc" id="_3de25ba3-1474-aafa-fb04-59bd58732ffc"></a><h3>B.1.3.<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>Literal data values</h3>

<p class="Sourcecode"><a name="_ac3f0e95-7a7b-0fb5-3442-30775baf6f57" id="_ac3f0e95-7a7b-0fb5-3442-30775baf6f57"></a><span class="nt">&lt;LiteralValue</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="na">dataType=</span><span class="s">http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#double</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="na">uom=</span><span class="s">"meter"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; 42.1<br/><span class="nt">&lt;/LiteralValue&gt;</span><br/><br/><span class="nt">&lt;LiteralValue</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="na">dataType=</span><span class="s">"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; ArableLand<br/><span class="nt">&lt;/LiteralValue&gt;</span></p>

</div>

<div><a name="_6a3a3e30-f155-343f-62cf-c20498fb5f0d" id="_6a3a3e30-f155-343f-62cf-c20498fb5f0d"></a><h3>B.1.4.<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>BoundingBox Data Description</h3>

<p class="Sourcecode"><a name="_99786bd1-b33e-508a-11fc-09d67600a3f3" id="_99786bd1-b33e-508a-11fc-09d67600a3f3"></a><span class="nt">&lt;wps:BoundingBoxData&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;wps:Format</span> <span class="na">mimeType=</span><span class="s">"text/plain"</span> <span class="na">default=</span><span class="s">"true"</span><span class="nt">/&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;wps:Format</span> <span class="na">mimeType=</span><span class="s">"text/xml"</span><span class="nt">/&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;wps:SupportedCRS</span> <span class="na">default=</span><span class="s">"true"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>EPSG:4326<span class="nt">&lt;/wps:SupportedCRS&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;wps:SupportedCRS&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0; http://www.opengis.net/def/crs/EPSG/0/4258<br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;/wps:SupportedCRS&gt;</span><br/><span class="nt">&lt;/wps:BoundingBoxData&gt;</span></p>

</div>

<div><a name="_c22ee0bb-d94f-ce74-350b-926aee8ff6f5" id="_c22ee0bb-d94f-ce74-350b-926aee8ff6f5"></a><h3>B.1.5.<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>BoundingBox Data Values</h3>

<p class="Sourcecode"><a name="_4bc8bc78-f9ab-8351-22c3-52dea78dccd2" id="_4bc8bc78-f9ab-8351-22c3-52dea78dccd2"></a><span class="nt">&lt;ows:BoundingBox</span> <span class="na">crs=</span><span class="s">"EPSG:4326"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:LowerCorner&gt;</span>51.9 7.0<span class="nt">&lt;/ows:LowerCorner&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:UpperCorner&gt;</span>53.0 8.0<span class="nt">&lt;/ows:UpperCorner&gt;</span><br/><span class="nt">&lt;/ows:BoundingBox&gt;</span><br/><br/><span class="nt">&lt;ows:BoundingBox</span><br/>&#xA0;&#xA0; <span class="na">crs=</span><span class="s">"http://www.opengis.net/def/crs/EPSG/0/4258"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:LowerCorner&gt;</span>51.9 7.0<span class="nt">&lt;/ows:LowerCorner&gt;</span><br/>&#xA0; <span class="nt">&lt;ows:UpperCorner&gt;</span>53.0 8.0<span class="nt">&lt;/ows:UpperCorner&gt;</span><br/><span class="nt">&lt;/ows:BoundingBox&gt;</span></p>

</div>
</div>
